-- Glitnir Priority Creditors to Receive $850 Million, Visir Says
-- B y   O m a r   R .   V a l d i m a r s s o n
-- 2012-01-18T09:45:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-18/glitnir-priority-creditors-to-receive-850-million-visir-says.html
Glitnir Bank hf’s priority creditors
will be paid 106 billion kronur ($850 million) by the end of
February according to a proposal from the failed lender’s
winding-up committee, Visir  reported , citing a letter to
creditors.  About 60 percent of the sum will be held in escrow until
disputes over claims have been resolved, according to the
Reykjavik-based news service. Glitnir’s payments will be made in
the Icelandic, Norwegian, U.S., U.K. currencies as well as
euros, Visir reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Omar R. Valdimarsson in Reykjavik 
